==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exacting
<hw>Ex*act"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Oppressive or unreasonably
severe in making demands or requiring the exact fulfillment of
obligations; harsh; severe.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A temper so
<xex>exacting</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>T. Arnold</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Ex*act"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Ex*act"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exaction</ent>⟦br⟧
